</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel box="[501,584,1994,2017]" pageId="3" pageNumber="60" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
(Scale = 10 mm) 8. Dorasal view, 9. Ventral view.
</paragraph>
